---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="Join ktprojects" active="join" bodyClass="bg-surface font-body text-on-surface">
  <main class="pt-24">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="relative px-8 py-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto overflow-hidden">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="z-10">
          <div
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-secondary-container/50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-6"
          >
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary animate-pulse"></span>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-primary font-label"
              >Spring 2026 Rush</span
            >
          </div>
          <h1
            class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-primary font-headline mb-6 leading-tight"
          >
            Rush <span class="text-on-surface">KTP</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-on-surface-variant max-w-lg mb-10 leading-relaxed">
            KTP rushes every Fall and Spring quarter. To rush, attend at least one info session
            and one other rush event. The application for Spring 2026 is live now.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <a
              href="https://uchicagoktp.com"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener"
              class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-primary-container text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold hover:brightness-110 transition-all shadow-lg"
            >
              Initialize Application
            </a>
            <a
              href={base + '/projects'}
              class="bg-surface-container-lowest ghost-border text-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-all"
            >
              View Our Work
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div
            class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg p-1 aspect-square relative overflow-hidden"
          >
            <img
              class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg opacity-90"
              alt="Modern high-tech laboratory"
              src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAQ-aVs-m9zyflUFCvXeu1lKT-jbWLlFTnIlzbLcaX895oQSlLvoDLohzDsw0tjGVqwrGRofRuAB4H_6lycgW65r1nL1lBcjwZ1eutaJCUdGg3puGkdqb3pn7iwqMQuv1oqFVL8vPxsI5sU5r8hisE-D3EOCSMMcAQWA8c4DACEtOS7qpY98HbcruOsGjOBOtZiiNCYqUcsJ5ThRL4ocwckfI0fKSsLyQnblFnAaEFGWnNwumd5-XyiDLRGHw4FGm3xBsVFRkSkPNxu"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-primary/20 to-transparent"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Role Cards -->
    <section class="bg-surface-container-low py-24">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-16 gap-6">
          <div>
            <h2
              class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-primary font-headline mb-4"
            >
              Who's Welcome
            </h2>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant max-w-md">
              KTP brothers come from every discipline on campus — there's no cookie-cutter ideal
              rushee. These are just some of the backgrounds represented in the Project Committee.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-right">
            <span class="text-6xl font-black text-primary/10">04</span>
            <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-outline -mt-4">
              Common Tracks
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
          <div
            class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-lg ghost-border hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-6">terminal</span>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-2">Engineer</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-6">
              Systems architecture and high-performance backend infrastructure.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span
                class="px-2 py-1 bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container text-[10px] font-bold uppercase rounded"
                >Rust</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-2 py-1 bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container text-[10px] font-bold uppercase rounded"
                >Go</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-2 py-1 bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container text-[10px] font-bold uppercase rounded"
                >WASM</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-lg ghost-border hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-6">architecture</span>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-2">Designer</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-6">
              Visual systems, kinetic UI components, and architectural logic.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span
                class="px-2 py-1 bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container text-[10px] font-bold uppercase rounded"
                >Figma</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-2 py-1 bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container text-[10px] font-bold uppercase rounded"
                >Motion</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-2 py-1 bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container text-[10px] font-bold uppercase rounded"
                >DesignOps</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-lg ghost-border hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-6">analytics</span>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-2">Researcher</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-6">
              Market analysis, protocol design, and behavioral game theory.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span
                class="px-2 py-1 bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container text-[10px] font-bold uppercase rounded"
                >Data</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-2 py-1 bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container text-[10px] font-bold uppercase rounded"
                >Math</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-2 py-1 bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container text-[10px] font-bold uppercase rounded"
                >Economy</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-lg ghost-border hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-6">monitoring</span>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-2">Quant</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-6">
              Algorithmic strategies and automated risk management systems.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span
                class="px-2 py-1 bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container text-[10px] font-bold uppercase rounded"
                >Python</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-2 py-1 bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container text-[10px] font-bold uppercase rounded"
                >C++</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-2 py-1 bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container text-[10px] font-bold uppercase rounded"
                >Alpha</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Process -->
    <section class="py-24 px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <h2
        class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-primary font-headline mb-4 text-center"
      >
        Spring 2026 Rush Events
      </h2>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-center max-w-xl mx-auto mb-16">
        All events in McCormick Lounge, 8:00–10:00 PM. Attend at least one info session and one
        other rush event to be considered.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6 bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg">
          <div
            class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-surface-container-lowest ghost-border flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shadow-sm"
          >
            <span class="text-2xl font-black text-primary">23</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-sm font-bold mb-1">Info Session 1</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-outline uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Mon March 23</p>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs">Get to know KTP.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6 bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg">
          <div
            class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-surface-container-lowest ghost-border flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shadow-sm"
          >
            <span class="text-2xl font-black text-primary">24</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-sm font-bold mb-1">Info Session 2</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-outline uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Tue March 24</p>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs">Same content, second chance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6 bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg">
          <div
            class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-surface-container-lowest ghost-border flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shadow-sm"
          >
            <span class="text-2xl font-black text-primary">25</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-sm font-bold mb-1">Color A Smile</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-outline uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Wed March 25</p>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs">
            Charity event — drawings for senior citizens and troops overseas.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6 bg-primary rounded-lg">
          <div
            class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-primary-container flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shadow-xl shadow-primary/20"
          >
            <span class="text-2xl font-black text-white">26</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-sm font-bold mb-1 text-white">Drop A Pin</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-white/70 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Thu March 26</p>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-xs">Speed-dating style — meet the brothers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Application CTA (form link anchor) -->
    <section id="apply" class="py-24 px-8">
      <div
        class="max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-primary-container rounded-xl p-12 md:p-20 text-center relative overflow-hidden"
      >
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">
            Ready to build the future?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-primary-fixed/80 text-lg mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            We are looking for individuals who prioritize precision over speed, and architecture
            over temporary fixes.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://uchicagoktp.com"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="inline-block bg-surface-container-lowest text-primary px-12 py-5 rounded-lg font-black text-lg uppercase tracking-widest hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all shadow-2xl"
          >
            Initialize Application
          </a>
          <div
            class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-8 text-white/60 font-label text-xs tracking-widest uppercase"
          >
            <span>Remote Ready</span>
            <span>UChicago Based</span>
            <span>Open Source</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section class="py-24 px-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2
        class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-primary font-headline mb-12 text-center"
      >
        Rush FAQ
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <details class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg p-6 group">
          <summary
            class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none font-bold text-on-surface"
          >
            Who can rush KTP?
            <span
              class="material-symbols-outlined text-outline group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"
              >expand_more</span
            >
          </summary>
          <div
            class="mt-4 text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-outline-variant/10 pt-4"
          >
            Anyone is allowed to rush KTP — we gladly accept (and encourage) rushees from all
            disciplines, years, and majors. Our only requirement is that you have at least 3
            quarters remaining as a full-time student in The College.
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg p-6 group">
          <summary
            class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none font-bold text-on-surface"
          >
            What does KTP look for in a rushee?
            <span
              class="material-symbols-outlined text-outline group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"
              >expand_more</span
            >
          </summary>
          <div
            class="mt-4 text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-outline-variant/10 pt-4"
          >
            There's no cookie-cutter "ideal" rushee — if there were, KTP wouldn't be the
            multi-talented, interdisciplinary organization that it is. We are an org united by our
            love for technology, and people who are truly passionate about tech are the ones who
            usually fit in best.
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg p-6 group">
          <summary
            class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none font-bold text-on-surface"
          >
            How often does rush happen?
            <span
              class="material-symbols-outlined text-outline group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"
              >expand_more</span
            >
          </summary>
          <div
            class="mt-4 text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-outline-variant/10 pt-4"
          >
            We typically rush during Fall and Spring quarters. If you miss one cycle, the next is
            only a few months away.
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg p-6 group">
          <summary
            class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none font-bold text-on-surface"
          >
            Can I rush KTP if I'm rushing another pre-professional frat?
            <span
              class="material-symbols-outlined text-outline group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"
              >expand_more</span
            >
          </summary>
          <div
            class="mt-4 text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-outline-variant/10 pt-4"
          >
            We encourage you to join only one pre-professional fraternity, but we welcome everyone
            to rush regardless. No judgment from us.
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg p-6 group">
          <summary
            class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none font-bold text-on-surface"
          >
            What is the Project Committee?
            <span
              class="material-symbols-outlined text-outline group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"
              >expand_more</span
            >
          </summary>
          <div
            class="mt-4 text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-outline-variant/10 pt-4"
          >
            The Project Committee is an internal subdivision of KTP inside the Technical
            Advancement pillar. It's a small group of brothers who build software together as a
            team — real projects with shipped outcomes, not just classwork.
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg p-6 group">
          <summary
            class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none font-bold text-on-surface"
          >
            Who do I contact if I have questions?
            <span
              class="material-symbols-outlined text-outline group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"
              >expand_more</span
            >
          </summary>
          <div
            class="mt-4 text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-outline-variant/10 pt-4"
          >
            Reach out at <a class="underline text-primary" href="mailto:uchicagoktp@gmail.com"
              >uchicagoktp@gmail.com</a
            > or DM us on Instagram
            <a
              class="underline text-primary"
              href="https://www.instagram.com/uchicagoktp"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener">@uchicagoktp</a
            >.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
